data.description: A spacious corner lot with beautiful landscaping and a clean brick exterior set the tone for what you'll discover inside! Enter the spacious and bright front living room with open sight lines into the dining and kitchen area, where you'll find an abundance of cabinetry and counter space along with stainless appliances. Bonus storage space can also be found in the large walk-in closet just off the living room. The separate family room with private entrance could easily be converted to a third bedroom or ideal office. Down the hall, the two spacious bedrooms, both with great natural light and hardwood flooring share the full bathroom. Relax and unwind in the private, fenced backyard highlighted by gorgeous trees and a bonus storage shed. Find peace of mind with a new furnace in Nov 2023! Make this one yours today!
